Task Turn Points

FIGURE 20 TASK TURN POINT TYPE DIALOG BOX.


FIGURE 21 BEER CAN AND FAI SECTORS.
Two types of task turn point observation zones are supported by the software, FAI sectors and "Beer Can"
sectors. "Beer can" turn points supplement the 90 °FAI sector with a specified radius sector centred on the
turn point. The type of turn point to be used and radius of the "beer can" can be specified using this dialog
box.
Once the glider is detected inside the observation zone, the next task turn point is automatically selected as
the current turn point.
